label chapter4_day6_route1:
    scene black
    with fade
    centered "Day 20 - Saturday 20th January."
    pause 1.0

    scene bg bedroom day
    play music hareka_theme fadein 0.5 fadeout 0.5 loop
    with fade
    "I wake up first, surprisingly."
    "I stand up, stretching, and look out of the window."
    "The weather looks pretty calm for January..."
    "I hear Hareka stirring."
    show hareka arbiter alt hair_down smile
    harekai "Good morning."
    my "Ah, good morning Hareka."
    my "Did you sleep well?"
    harekai "Yeah, actually..."
    my "I told you so! Sleeping in a proper bed makes a huge difference..."
    harekai "Ahaha, yeah..."
    harekai "Let's get breakfast."
    my "Okay!"

    scene bg kitchen day
    show hareka arbiter alt hair_down smile
    with fade
    "We head into the kitchen, and she makes us both some breakfast."
    "She sits down next to me, and we eat."
    show hareka arbiter alt hair_down eyes_closed smile
    harekai "Sigh..."
    my "What's wrong?"
    harekai "Oh, I'm just thinking a bit."
    show hareka arbiter alt hair_down smile
    harekai "I just find it funny how I fought my ass off for this job, but I really hate it."
    my "You find that funny?"
    harekai "Well, yeah... It's just ironic."
    "She chuckles."
    "I sigh."
    my "You can always step down. It's not like anyone's gonna be mad if you calmly hand it to someone else."
    harekai "No way."
    "She shakes her head."
    harekai "That isn't an option anymore."
    show hareka arbiter alt hair_down eyes_closed smile
    harekai "I'll just have to bare the consequences of my actions..."
    "I feel a pang of guilt."
    "Yet she's still smiling."
    "How...?"

    scene bg bedroom day
    show hareka arbiter alt hair_down smile
    with fade
    "We return to the bedroom once we've done with our food."
    harekai "Right, time to do my hair."
    pause 0.5
    show hareka arbiter alt smile
    "She brushes through her hair before tying it up in the usual style."
    harekai "Done!"
    my "Ready to go to work?"
    harekai "Ready as I'll ever be..."

    scene bg office day
    play music arbiter_office_theme fadein 0.5 fadeout 0.5 loop
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed smile
    with flash
    "We arrive at the Office."
    my "I can help you out with work, if you'd like."
    show hareka arbiter alt smile
    harekai "That would be helpful. Thanks!"
    my "You're welcome."
    "We get to work, me helping her with proofreading and a bit of idea brainstorming."
    "The morning flies by, and eventually, lunchtime arrives."
    
    scene bg cafeteria day
    show hareka arbiter alt normal at left
    show mora arbiter normal at right
    with fade
    "Hareka & Mora" "..."
    "Once again, they find themselves in conflict."
    "I sigh."
    my "I should just ban you both from being in the same room or something."
    mora "You don't have that kind of power."
    my "I know..."
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed normal
    harekai "We need to resolve this."
    my "Yes, you definitely should."
    mora "I'd be happy to fight you to the death."
    my "Oi! Back off already!"
    show mora arbiter eyes_closed normal
    mora "God it was a joke."
    my "Ugh..."
    show hareka arbiter alt normal
    harekai "Mora, what exactly is it you hate about me?"
    show mora arbiter normal
    mora "I just don't want you in charge."
    mora "It's nothing against {i}you{/i} I guess..."
    harekai "Is it because you were supposed to monitor Alex?"
    my "Huh- She was??"
    harekai "Yes."
    my "Ah..."
    "Well that explains a lot."
    show mora arbiter eyes_closed normal
    mora "I suppose."
    harekai "Thought so."
    harekai "Come sit with us. We can talk through it while eating."
    show mora arbiter normal
    mora "Really?"
    harekai "I wouldn't say it if I didn't want it."
    mora "Oh... Okay."
    harekai "You don't mind, do you? She just needs comforting."
    "Hareka whispers to me."
    my "Nah, I don't mind."
    "I reply."
    "We order our food and bring it over to the table, sitting down."
    my "So uh... Why did Mora end up not monitoring me?"
    harekai "It's complicated."
    my "Oh..."
    my "Can't this be resolved really easily, though?"
    harekai "What do you mean?"
    my "Why not have Mora monitor me alongside you?"
    show mora with vpunch
    "Mora chokes."
    mora "*cough cough*"
    my "Are you okay?!"
    mora "What the hell are you saying??"
    mora "Are you crazy?!"
    my "Is it really that bad of an idea...?"
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed normal
    harekai "It isn't a bad idea, no."
    harekai "However, the system doesn't work like that."
    my "Oh..."
    mora "You know what, it's fine."
    show hareka arbiter alt normal
    harekai "What is?"
    mora "You being with her."
    mora "You probably did a better job than me in the end."
    harekai "Well, I wouldn't say that..."
    mora "Are you happy, Hareka?"
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed normal
    harekai "..."
    show mora arbiter eyes_closed normal
    mora "I see."
    mora "Seems you never will be satisfied."
    mora "All you ever do is take."
    mora "You took the company over, you took over my assignment with Alex, and now you're going to take away her happiness."
    my "Uhm-"
    my "I'm not entirely sure what's going on, but I'm pretty happy here-"
    show mora arbiter normal
    mora "Are you really?"
    my "Yes!"
    my "I'm happy spending every day with her, helping her out..."
    my "She may not seem it but she is a nice person!"
    my "And I only want her to be happy..."
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed blush
    harekai "..."
    mora "Woah."
    mora "She's gone totally red..."
    harekai "You know what..."
    play music love_theme fadein 0.5 fadeout 1.0 loop
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed blush smile
    harekai "I think that's all I needed to hear..."
    show hareka arbiter alt blush smile
    harekai "I am happy, Mora. I am so happy."
    harekai "Please don't take this away from me now. Please."
    show mora arbiter eyes_closed normal
    mora "..."
    mora "I can't argue with... that..."
    mora "Hmph."
    hide mora with dissolve
    "Mora storms off."
    "I turn to Hareka."
    my "Are you okay?"
    harekai "I am... so happy..."
    my "Ah... I'm glad about that."
    "We finish our lunch in comfortable silence."

    scene bg office day
    show hareka arbiter alt smile
    with fade
    "We return to the office, and continue with work."
    "She looks a lot happier... I'm glad for her."
    "{b}{u}A few hours later...{/u}{/b}"
    "We finally finish."
    "Hareka packs up and turns to me."
    harekai "Shall we head back?"
    my "Yep!"

    scene bg bedroom day
    play music hareka_theme fadein 0.5 fadeout 0.5 loop
    show hareka arbiter alt smile
    with flash
    "We return home."
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed smile
    harekai "You know what..."
    my "What?"
    harekai "I think I'm gonna take tomorrow off."
    "That caught me off guard."
    my "Really?"
    show hareka arbiter alt smile
    harekai "It's Sunday, most people don't work on Sundays. The office would be a lot more quiet, so I would be fine not attending."
    my "Ah..."
    my "Well, if you want to, that's fine."
    harekai "Yes."

    scene bg kitchen day
    show hareka arbiter alt smile
    with fade
    "We head into the kitchen to make dinner together."
    "She hums to herself as she works."
    "I laugh."
    my "You act so cute sometimes."
    show hareka arbiter alt blush smile
    harekai "Thanks..."
    show hareka arbiter alt smile
    "We finish making dinner, and sit down to eat."
    harekai "We should go somewhere tomorrow."
    my "Oh?"
    my "Where were you thinking?"
    harekai "I'd like to go to the park."
    harekai "I know it's simple, but I think it'd be nice."
    my "Yeah, that sounds like a good idea!"
    harekai "Yay!"
    "I smile."
    my "I'm looking forward to it, then."
    harekai "So am I..."

    scene bg bedroom evening
    show hareka arbiter alt smile
    with fade
    "When we finish, we return to the room."
    my "I guess it's time for bed."
    my "I don't wanna be tired for tomorrow."
    harekai "Yep..."
    my "Don't you stay up too late either, okay?"
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed smile
    harekai "Heh, okay."
    my "Good."
    "I pat her."
    show hareka arbiter alt eyes_closed blush smile
    harekai "Mm..."
    my "Goodnight, Hareka."
    harekai "Goodnight."
    window hide
    play music chapter1_theme fadein 0.5 fadeout 0.5 loop
    $ chapter4_day7_route1_avail = True
    scene black
    with fade
    centered "End of day."
